tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-30M","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":18059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/05\/merchants-wicked-unless-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11580,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Trade: Merchants with the wicked, unless they fear Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah ibn Rafi' reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0said, \u201cVerily, merchants will be raised on the Day of Resurrection with the wicked, except for those who fear Allah, behave righteously, and are truthful.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1210 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0646 \u0631\u0627\u0641\u0639\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/adab-order-for-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":11580,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Etiquette of order for supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while Abu Bakr and Umar were with him. When I sat down, I began by praising Allah, then sending blessings upon the Prophet, then supplicating for myself. The Prophet said, \u201cAsk and you will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41294,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/honor-suppress-rage\/","url_meta":{"origin":11580,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Honor in the Hereafter for suppressing rage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever suppresses his rage, even though he could unleash it, Allah will summon him on the Day of Resurrection before the heads of all creation to choose whichever maiden he wishes.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2021 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14615,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/06\/dua-tashahhud-allah-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":11580,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Supplication at the end of sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, heard a man supplicating in his prayer, and he did not send blessing upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cThis man has rushed.\u201d Then, the Prophet called for the man or some others, and he said, \u201cWhen one of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"clas